de.tum.bgu.lfk.datahandling.table

Class Table

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.tum.bgu.lfk.datahandling.table.Table

  • public class Table
extends java.lang.Object
    a table class to use within processing and processing js. based on the table class from ben fry and ceasy reas out of their book "Visualizing Data" (OReilly)

    to make a processing class JavaScript compatible see at how to make the table JavaScript compatible
    Since:
    12.06.2014
    Version:
    0.0.2
    Author:
    Mathias Jahnke, Technische Universität München, Department of Cartography
